{"id":769953855,"lang":"cpp","lang_name":"C++","time":"1 year, 5 months","timestamp":1660109897,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"73 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/769953855/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Delete Operation for Two Strings","memory":"12.2 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    int minDistance(string word1, string word2) {\n        int l1=word1.length(),l2=word2.length();\n        vector<vector<int>>dp(l1+1,vector<int>(l2+1,0));\n        for(int i=0;i<l1+1;i++)\n        {\n            for(int j=0;j<l2+1;j++)\n            {\n                if(i==0 || j==0)\n                    dp[i][j]=0;\n                else if(word1[i-1]==word2[j-1])\n                    dp[i][j]=dp[i-1][j-1]+1;\n                else\n                {\n                    dp[i][j]=max(dp[i-1][j],dp[i][j-1]);\n                }\n            }\n        }\n        return l1+l2-2*dp[l1][l2];\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"delete-operation-for-two-strings","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
